        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59167/7126_59167_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "That is out of the question.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59167_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59167/7126_59167_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "My friend, return to literary activity!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59167_000013_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59167/7126_59167_000013_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "I can neither walk, nor eat, nor sleep.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59167_000013_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59167/7126_59167_000013_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "It is wearisome even to repeat it all!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59167_000013_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59167/7126_59167_000013_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "My friend-great writer of our Russian land, listen to my request!...",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59167_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59167/7126_59167_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "He was a man whom it was possible to disgust.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59167_000014_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59167/7126_59167_000014_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "One can guess exactly the frame of mind he was in when, in the course of an argument with Dostoevsky, he said: \"You see, I consider myself a German.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59167_000015_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59167/7126_59167_000015_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "He had that sense of truth which always upsets the orthodox.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59167_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59167/7126_59167_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "almost caresses, from people of the opposite camp, from enemies. This confused me, wounded me; but my conscience did not reproach me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59167_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59167/7126_59167_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "This is bound to be the fate of every artist who takes his political party or his church, or any other propagandist group to which he belongs, as his subject.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59167_000017_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59167/7126_59167_000017_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "He \"simply did not know how to work otherwise,\" as he said.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59167_000017_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59167/7126_59167_000017_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "He had always to draw from the life.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59167_000017_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59167/7126_59167_000017_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "\"I ought to confess,\" he once wrote, \"that I never attempted to create a type without having, not an idea, but a living person, in whom the various elements were harmonized together, to work from.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59167_000018_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59167/7126_59167_000018_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "It would be foolish, I know, to pretend to sum up Dostoevsky as a contortionist; but he has that element in him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59167_000018_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59167/7126_59167_000018_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "He was one of the first great novelists to endow his women with independence of soul. With the majority of novelists, women are sexual or sentimental accidents.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "He is so obviously not a god.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "He is a man and a medical doctor.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000004_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000004_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "At the same time he is a theme that they were bound to treat.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "There is bound to be a break in the meanest life.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "He does not run sympathy as a \"stunt\" like so many popular novelists.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "He has the most unbiassed attitude, I think, of any author in the world.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000006_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000006_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "He portrays his characters instead of labelling them; but the portrait itself is the judgment.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000006_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000006_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "His attitude to a large part of life might be described as one of good-natured disgust.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "She would sleep every day till two or three o'clock; she had her coffee and lunch in bed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "She waked up every morning with the one thought of \"pleasing.\" It was the aim and object of her life.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "She wanted every day to enchant, to captivate, to drive men crazy.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "A few strokes of cruelty are added to the portrait:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "A crow ...",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "Who's there?\" she called suddenly, hearing my steps.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "\"It's i\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "And in the winter they will probably go abroad,\" she added after a pause.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "\"'God sent ... the crow ... a piece ... of cheese....' Have you written it?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000023_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000023_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "But, though he often makes his people beautiful in their sorrow, he more often than not sets their sad figures against a common and ugly background.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000028_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000028_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "'You're such a pretty dear!'\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000029_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000029_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "He is a writer who desires above all things to see what men and women are really like-to extenuate nothing and to set down naught in malice.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7126_59175_000029_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7126/59175/7126_59175_000029_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7126",
        "content": "As a result, he is a pessimist, but a pessimist who is black without being bitter.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    }
]